{"id":41833,"date":"2024-01-27T10:30:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-27T05:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=41833"},"modified":"2023-01-31T11:35:48","modified_gmt":"2023-01-31T06:05:48","slug":"oversized-chair-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/oversized-chair-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Oversized Chair Designs For Extra Comfort And Cosiness"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>These big, oversized chair designs are a fashionable way to up the comfort and style quotient of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you wanted an oversized chair all to yourself, the kind that you always go back to \u2014 be it for your movie nights, journaling me-times or even more so a reading cocoon? We have listed some of our personal favourite big, oversized chair designs that are a class apart, and you\u2019ll love them all the more. Without further ado, let\u2019s dive right in!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oversized Swivel Chair In Blush Pink For Your Living Space<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your living room can be a great place to create a multi-functional area, one that allows you to experience and create multitudes of memories. With that being said, having a space that celebrates the joys of being indoors, in comfort and having an ambience can be quite a calming experience for you and your family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As seen in the image, this living room showcases a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/seating-ideas-for-home\/\">cosy seating arrangement <\/a>with its two large pink swivel chairs. What\u2019s even greater about this arrangement is how every aspect of the living room blends well into the setting, like the indoor plants, the tall bookshelf unit that extends into a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">home office<\/a> as well as the chaise lounge that\u2019s perfect for movie nights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215137\/Oversized-Swivel-chair-design-for-your-living-space.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized Swivel chair design for your living space\" class=\"wp-image-41841\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215137\/Oversized-Swivel-chair-design-for-your-living-space.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215137\/Oversized-Swivel-chair-design-for-your-living-space-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215137\/Oversized-Swivel-chair-design-for-your-living-space-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215137\/Oversized-Swivel-chair-design-for-your-living-space-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Swivel chairs for added comfort in the living room\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oversized Round Cuddle Chair For The Perfect Reading Experience<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dissecting your room into varied sections as per the needs of the family members in the house is a fine way to create dedicated spots in the living space. Starting with this beautiful living room, as seen in the image, which features a strikingly pretty coastal palette of whites and blues.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What\u2019s so cool about this living space is the oversized round cuddle chair and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/accent-chairs-for-living-room\/\">accent chair<\/a> for coffee evenings, book reading sessions, work or simply a quick tete-a-tete with your close friend.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215130\/Oversized-Round-Cuddle-Chair-for-your-reading-experience.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized Round Cuddle Chair for your reading experience\" class=\"wp-image-41840\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215130\/Oversized-Round-Cuddle-Chair-for-your-reading-experience.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215130\/Oversized-Round-Cuddle-Chair-for-your-reading-experience-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215130\/Oversized-Round-Cuddle-Chair-for-your-reading-experience-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215130\/Oversized-Round-Cuddle-Chair-for-your-reading-experience-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A cuddle chair for the perfect bonding time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Space saving home interiors with 20% extra space\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/26112643\/space-saving-home-interiors-with-20-extra-space-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Lovely Pastel Diamond-Tufted Folding Sleeper Chair In A Bright Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a guest over with no room for them to stay the night can be quite a daunting experience. Times like these are when you consider certain <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/space-saving-design\/\">space-saving home interiors<\/a> features that allow you to transform your space, be it day or night.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This lovely room features a stunning diamond-tufted folding sleeper chair in pink that can simply turn into a single bed at night, should you have guests for a fun sleepover.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215124\/Oversized-sleeper-chair-design-in-Pastel-for-guests.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized sleeper chair design in Pastel for guests\" class=\"wp-image-41839\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215124\/Oversized-sleeper-chair-design-in-Pastel-for-guests.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215124\/Oversized-sleeper-chair-design-in-Pastel-for-guests-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215124\/Oversized-sleeper-chair-design-in-Pastel-for-guests-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215124\/Oversized-sleeper-chair-design-in-Pastel-for-guests-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A folding sleeper chair for when guests come over<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mid-Century Living Space With A Pastel Oversized Folding Chair<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mid-century home interiors carry a charm of their own with their wooden accents, high-sprung furnishings and an eclectic vintage interior style. Just like this lovely room that features a combination of mid-century with modern elements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What\u2019s so cool about this space is the pastel blue oversized folding chair that can very well transform into a reclining chair or even better a sleeper chair. This is a perfect addition to this room as it features a bookshelf and the chair can work great for a comfortable read. Not to mention that the table lamp, wabi-sabi side table and open rack shelf unit simply strike a balance between mid-century and modern.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215119\/Oversized-Folding-Chair-design-in-Pastel.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized Folding Chair design in Pastel\" class=\"wp-image-41838\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215119\/Oversized-Folding-Chair-design-in-Pastel.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215119\/Oversized-Folding-Chair-design-in-Pastel-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215119\/Oversized-Folding-Chair-design-in-Pastel-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215119\/Oversized-Folding-Chair-design-in-Pastel-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A pastel oversized folding chair by the window<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Big Oversized Chair With Pull-Out Mattress For Guest Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Living in a compact apartment comes with its own space limitations, but there are many ways to get around this. One of them is choosing the right furnishing and seating arrangements for the space. For instance, a Murphy bed that can be tucked in when not needed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if Murphy beds aren\u2019t your first choice, you can simply switch to a daybed or an oversized chair (like the one in the image) with a pull-out mattress for your guest rooms. Add an ottoman, an area rug, a side table and a lamp along with shelves and a wardrobe to complete the look and you are good to go.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215114\/Oversized-chair-with-pull-out-mattress.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized chair with pull-out mattress\" class=\"wp-image-41837\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215114\/Oversized-chair-with-pull-out-mattress.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215114\/Oversized-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215114\/Oversized-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215114\/Oversized-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A chair that turns into a guest bed when needed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End to end modular home interiors for indian homes\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/26111433\/End-to-end-modular-home-interiors-for-indian-homes-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oversized Hanging Armchair For Your Zen Corner&#8217;s Seating Area<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a space all to yourself for your me-time, meditative sessions and quiet times is lovely. However, how you choose to decorate this space can simply make or break it. A quick tip for creating your zen corner would be to allow the space to have a breathing area, and by that we mean allowing enough space and legroom for you to move around. Don\u2019t add too many elements, but enough to keep it light and cosy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, this zen corner features a wicker floor lamp, a tufted floor seat as well as an oversized hanging armchair blending in with the grey ottoman. You can use this space, as it deems fit, for yoga, morning meditations, journaling or simply reading a book.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215107\/Oversized-hanging-armchair-for-your-zen-corner.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized hanging armchair for your zen corner\" class=\"wp-image-41836\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215107\/Oversized-hanging-armchair-for-your-zen-corner.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215107\/Oversized-hanging-armchair-for-your-zen-corner-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215107\/Oversized-hanging-armchair-for-your-zen-corner-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215107\/Oversized-hanging-armchair-for-your-zen-corner-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A beautiful zen corner for quality me-time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Oversized Twin Chairs For A Great Movie Night Experience<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For newly-wed couples that love to binge-watch, movie nights can be a fun place to start. You could consider investing in oversized twin chairs, as shown in the image, for the perfect movie experience and pair it with a comfortable ottoman that doubles as a coffee table.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a few art frames, ambient lights and decorative pillows to the space with a wide-angle TV and you are good to go.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215100\/Oversized-twin-chair-design-for-a-great-movie-night.jpg\" alt=\"Oversized twin chair design for a great movie night\" class=\"wp-image-41835\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215100\/Oversized-twin-chair-design-for-a-great-movie-night.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215100\/Oversized-twin-chair-design-for-a-great-movie-night-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215100\/Oversized-twin-chair-design-for-a-great-movie-night-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/28215100\/Oversized-twin-chair-design-for-a-great-movie-night-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A comfortable entertainment area for couples<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And with that, we come to an end of our 